<item>
            <title>[LU-6609] recovery-small test_26a : FAIL: remove sub-test dirs failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6609</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== recovery-small test 26a: evict dead exports == 00:18:10 (1373343490)
starting with 4 OST exports
fail_loc=0x505
Waiting 55 secs for update
Waiting 45 secs for update
Waiting 35 secs for update
Waiting 25 secs for update
Waiting 15 secs for update
Updated after 45s: wanted &apos;3&apos; got &apos;3&apos;
fail_loc=0x0
Resetting fail_loc on all nodes...done.
PASS 26a (50s)
== recovery-small test complete, duration 57 sec == 00:19:00 (1373343540)
 recovery-small : @@@@@@ FAIL: remove sub-test dirs failed &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It can&apos;t remove dirs because import after evicting is still invalid:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;00000100:00000200:0.0:1385996752.852317:0:1047:0:(client.c:1170:ptlrpc_import_delay_req()) @@@ IMP_INVALID  req@ffff880051dd9b80 x1453320200794608/t0(0) o101-&amp;gt;lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff88005d78ac00@10.3.0.65@tcp:12/10 lens 552/1016 e 0 to 0 dl 0 ref 2 fl Rpc:/0/ffffffff rc 0/-1&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test should wait for import state FULL before remove sub-test dirs.&lt;br/&gt;
Decrement of export number may be caused by net issues.&lt;br/&gt;
In suggested patch test passes only when import state becomes EVICTED.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
